description:
The issues in the book of Daniel are worship and obedience. The issues in the last days will be worship and obedience. It is important that each of us remains faithful to God. Do you want to be loyal and obedient to God now, so that you, too, might be loyal and true to God when the difficult times come? Find out how in our new program, "Daniel 3 - Facing the Fiery Furnace"
